{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where, at the camp?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] No care at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Couldn't go to work, they were killed immediately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no-- no time for that, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the women-- the women, of course were given something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know, either something that they add to the soups, or-- because I don't remember getting any pills, so it had to be in a form that they put into the soups that we were getting that no woman menstruated in camp.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister-- well, I was the first one that came down with typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the reason I survived, I think, was that was this commandant was sick himself away in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But from the time he came back, there were no survivors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once somebody got sick, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He even fooled us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a barrack, number five, that, if we're sick and we can't go to work, and if we're going to that barrack, he'll see to it that we get help, and get well, and be able to go back to work.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody survived there more than two days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He came and killed them at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then everybody was afraid to go to barrack five.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When did I escape?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I escaped in the fall of, I think, '43.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think '43.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, and that was-- we were a small group, going back-- not on our shift, so we were about, boy, I would say 20 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My sister, I had a chance to send out to-- see, she was very sick with-- with diarrhea and-- very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- and this man offered to take her out and possibly take her to a doctor, bring her back to camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
